  "description": "Turns a bunch of players in the plushies!",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/colon3smp\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"colon3smp\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://www.supersnetwork.com/tags/created_for_colon3smp_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/plushie-nonsense\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"modrinth\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/hNv2yu4PKh\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"discord-plural\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/discord-plural_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n---\n\nThis mod adds a collection of plushies based on players from my Discord server. Somehow, through mysterious and probably unsafe means, they have been turned into soft, squishy decorations. Gather them all and decorate your world with tiny plush versions of my friends.\n\nThis mod was inspired by the [Ratatouille mod on Modrinth](https://modrinth.com/mod/ratatouille).\n\n---\n\n<a href=\"https://billing.bytebuilders.co.za/aff/SUPER\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"bytebuilders\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://www.supersnetwork.com/tags/sponsored_by_bytebuilders_1.svg\">\n</a>",
